<h2>Why is Ferrari the best?</h2>
<p> Because, since the beginning of Formula one, they have been consistently good. With talented members
    and awesome cars, they are always at the top of their game. Although their strategies seem to be
    rather useless lately, they have good cars that function well. As Enzo Ferrari once said "Ask
    a child to draw a car, and he will draw it red." Ferrari is elite.
</p>

